{"tid":2338707,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"華納撤港丨香港華納電影不敵武肺 下月結業解散全體員工","createTime":"2020-12-24T07:35:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-24T21:48:33.000Z","uid":212249,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"10a7dbb9c3c10d70497f11789a7085c94c3687cc","tid":2338707,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T07:35:53.000Z","msg":"華納媒體（Warner Media）因為武漢肺炎大流行導致電影票房、有線電視訂閱和電視廣告的收入流失，並於今年10月傳出重組，為求將成本降低多達20%。加上早前作出驚人舉動，將下年所有新戲放上串流頻道HBO Max，可知其經濟狀況有相當嚴重問題。今日就有消息指，華納的香港部門將全面撤出，並會解散全體員工，成為香港電影業第一滴血。<br />\n<br />\n華納兄弟電影公司作出重大改組，據消息指，他們將會與環球影業合作，在多個地區「兩個只能活一個」，只留下其中一間公司負責兩間的所有電影。至於香港方面，以後電影發行及宣傳，將交由環球影業負責，香港區華納兄弟所有員工都被解散，涉及10多名員工，當中3，4人會幫手完成明年發行的《神奇女俠1984》才正式離職。據知，華納自93、94年離開香港洲立，在港自設在發行公司至今。《蘋果》已向華納兄弟查詢，對方表示沒有回應。"},{"pid":"6570aacfed9fb8249aa0bc5dd6e64c77143751e7","tid":2338707,"uid":212249,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T07:36:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201224/ZWZYDQXZHBHUNIMAJEEE7KE4NQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201224%2FZWZYDQXZHBHUNIMAJEEE7KE4NQ%2F&d=otIFGLHjmDp%2FicXUVK76MfdnC8dk%2FAL47v0imjzWEG4%3D&h=c14f2ee4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201224%2FZWZYDQXZHBHUNIMAJEEE7KE4NQ%2F&h=2f4bc14e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201224/ZWZYDQXZHBHUNIMAJEEE7KE4NQ/</a>"},{"pid":"3636b1dfc82c88dc506e0be61f2783a87233f040","tid":2338707,"uid":66202,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T07:41:20.000Z","msg":"國安法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17235a21b8f1e8d049ef64ae73393d6191bd9aac","tid":2338707,"uid":3189,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T07:49:23.000Z","msg":"點解香港人永遠比人炒先？"},{"pid":"591909a18e86cd41db49f43b1787504079517902","tid":2338707,"uid":196450,"like":5,"dislike":1,"sc